  "texts": [
    "By using the 𝑇𝐶𝑃, monoBERT + 𝑑𝑢𝑜𝐵𝐸𝑅𝑇 𝑆𝑈 𝑀 achieved the best performance.",
    "monoBERT + 𝑑𝑢𝑜𝐵𝐸𝑅𝑇 𝑀𝐴𝑋 delivered the worst performance on the development set, 6% worse than that of 𝐵𝐸𝑅𝑇 𝐵𝑎𝑠𝑒.",
    "In addition, Manuscript submitted to ACM 𝐵𝐸𝑅𝑇 𝐵𝑎𝑠𝑒 outperformed 𝐵𝐸𝑅𝑇 𝐿𝑎𝑠𝑡 -𝐼𝑛𝑡, 𝐵𝐸𝑅𝑇 𝑀𝑢𝑙𝑡𝑖-𝐼𝑛𝑡, and 𝐵𝐸𝑅𝑇 𝑇 𝑒𝑟𝑚-𝑇 𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠.",
    "Furthermore, Nogueira et al.",
    "applied the [CLS] embedding of the last layer, which is similar to that of 𝐵𝐸𝑅𝑇 Last-Int."
  ],
